{"tid":1285523,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"香港人——別來無恙？","createTime":"2019-07-04T15:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T21:12:51.000Z","uid":274180,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"05bbe32d48c3f19c0a27e1b01c34edecec4a8b01","tid":1285523,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"你老母賣香港 而港豬 恭賀<br />\n有偉聰做一哥 全責傳 停帶<br />\n何君妖不服 出錢擺局<br />\n而啊麟擔心 再係咁 靠靜香<br />\n<br />\n我老母問香港 維穩衰邊樣<br />\n個議會爛玻璃 無法被忘記<br />\n話幾位死仕 收錢搞事<br />\n旁人攜著子女遊行<br />\n我問媽媽有沒睇要聞<br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥亂屈不辨白<br />\n個柒婆未識得入閘<br />\n修港法護中央<br />\n無懼香港應國難<br />\n啲警察亂開槍謾罵<br />\n鬧自由閪佢冇號碼<br />\n唔自責 唔負責<br />\n耶穌都高攀<br />\nhallelujah<br />\n<br />\n你戴起白絲帶 罷工兼休學<br />\n個政府話鳩知 唔去理會你<br />\n被家超羞辱 港英恥辱<br />\n誰說了特首要為民<br />\n你是否只愛護中國人<br />\n<br />\n鄭月娥亂鳩噏獨白<br />\n個柒婆未識得入閘<br />\n修黨法護中央<br />\n無懼香港對國難<br />\n啲警棍亂揮打亂發<br />\n百萬人街裏去問責<br />\n唔係我 （鄭月娥）唔係我（張建宗）<br />\n問警方一哥<br />\n一哥說恰當<br />\n<br />\n警總冰冷牆壁 怎麼寫滿彌哀<br />\n夢內畫黑的相 為何林奠發著呆<br />\n周街反對傳單 參選講過離開<br />\n實係上帝搞錯<br />\n<br />\n點解條木契柒婆認衰都站立<br />\n鄭月娥自尊心泛濫<br />\n呢三個柒姑碌<br />\n隨便講稿當對話<br />\n鄭月娥為港添混亂<br />\n有問題西過界就算<br />\n渠務署 民事署 <br />\n唯唯不兜圈<br />\n金鐘裏清算"},{"pid":"ec6d2a84004fc06d417d4132c558cac62bcc03d9","tid":1285523,"uid":204352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"strong post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d600e3edd13d2b5dcc1f291e033e4625e4a41f8","tid":1285523,"uid":260835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91edf357fd9680cc178cfe9d95b5178bea046e0","tid":1285523,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec6d2a84004fc06d417d4132c558cac62bcc03d9","tid":1285523,"uid":204352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:22:49.000Z","msg":"strong post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:29:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062d5cbb5bb0745f5cf79d64aba411110b96fa83","tid":1285523,"uid":86723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"hallelujah 笑出聲"},{"pid":"33829951b2550297a82cd35116efac180b2b56ed","tid":1285523,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"062d5cbb5bb0745f5cf79d64aba411110b96fa83","tid":1285523,"uid":86723,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T15:48:08.000Z","msg":"hallelujah 笑出聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:15:40.000Z","msg":"幫下佢手見耶穌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859ba8a7271651627b681f01e30113484f214cdf","tid":1285523,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"推到陳柏宇上勁歌唱"},{"pid":"24a69302d9fb04d4103b32e09b442f25a0c0574f","tid":1285523,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T22:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好意思借個位<br />\n<br />\n［唔好中計］深夜個「提防左膠」post係分化私怨post，請大家幫忙努力負評<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1286211\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1286211</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3ea76a555a54fa4a1015fae3d57f6f44eb4978a8","tid":1285523,"uid":274180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859ba8a7271651627b681f01e30113484f214cdf","tid":1285523,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"推到陳柏宇上勁歌唱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T02:34:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唱完仲見唔見到佢？"},{"pid":"0b1b648b89811518